modName: The Art of The Lucerne and Bec De Corbin

Ebony Lucerne & Bec De Corbin
Orcish Lucerne & Bec De Corbin

Steel Lucerne & Bec De Corbin

:-:Insert amazing title here:-:
The Bec De Corbins is stronger than the maces, with a longer reach and a slower swingtime
The Lucernes is stronger than the warhammers, with a longer reach and a slower swingtime
Thats all, yey
